org.ctoolkit.restapi.client

Interface UploadMediaRequest<T>


  • public interface UploadMediaRequest<T>
    The upload media request as wrapper of media content and associated resource. Gives a possibility to this resource to be either inserted or updated.
    Author:
    Aurel Medvegy
